173
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,550
They’re waiting for you.

174
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:17,400
Let’s go.

175
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,190
Yes.

176
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:29,840
Hua made this tea especially for you.

177
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:31,600
Please have a taste, Crown Princess.

178
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,190
It’s as good as I thought.

179
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,430
Well,

180
00:09:44,430 --> 00:09:45,480
it’s about time.

181
00:09:46,190 --> 00:09:48,240
Where’s Princess Royal?

182
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:52,120
Grandmother is still dressing herself up

183
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,240
to look proper when His Majesty arrives.

184
00:09:55,070 --> 00:09:56,360
I’ll go assist her

185
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,760
so that she won’t be late.

186
00:10:06,070 --> 00:10:08,030
You two take the back door

187
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:09,400
and get Grandmother’s
physician Zhang here.

188
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:09,950
Yes.

189
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,270
All rise.

190
00:10:15,430 --> 00:10:16,880
Thank you, Your Majesty.

191
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:22,120
We’re having a family banquet,
not in court.

192
00:10:22,310 --> 00:10:23,120
Just relax.

193
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,120
Be seated, everyone.

194
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:29,910
How’s the preparation?

195
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,790
Your Majesty,

196
00:10:32,310 --> 00:10:34,950
guards here have been swapped over

197
00:10:35,270 --> 00:10:37,670
to make way for our secret agents

198
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,430
to search for the Tiger Tally.

199
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:40,670
I see.

200
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,840
Zhang,

201
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:48,400
the banquet seems different from before.

202
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:49,670
You must’ve put in a lot of effort.

203
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:52,030
I’ll reward you handsomely.

204
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:56,520
Thank you, Father.

205
00:10:57,190 --> 00:10:58,910
It’s just that

206
00:10:59,310 --> 00:11:00,550
Rong Xia drafted the speech.

207
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:02,070
I don’t think

208
00:11:02,430 --> 00:11:04,000
I should read it.

209
00:11:04,190 --> 00:11:04,950
Zhang!

210
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,120
Huai.

211
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:15,030
Your Majesty.

212
00:11:15,190 --> 00:11:16,840
Where’s Princess Royal?

213
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:19,190
I’ve carefully

214
00:11:19,190 --> 00:11:20,400
chosen a gift for her.

215
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,550
If Mother knows

216
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:23,550
you’ve come with a gift,

217
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,360
she’ll be even more excited.

218
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,640
I’m sure

219
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,840
she’s tidying up as we speak.

220
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:30,880
Please have some drinks first

221
00:11:30,950 --> 00:11:33,120
and congratulate her once she arrives.

222
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:36,760
Alright. Let the banquet begin.

223
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:40,400
What are you doing here?

224
00:11:44,430 --> 00:11:45,070
Princess.

225
00:11:45,070 --> 00:11:47,190
Madam Chang, what happened?

226
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:50,480
Grandmother! Is she alright?

227
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:54,760
She’s been sick for a while
without telling anyone

228
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:57,240
because she knows once it gets out,

229
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,400
the Xies will have no scruples

230
00:11:58,430 --> 00:12:00,640
about ganging up on your family.

231
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:04,550
How did you know?

232
00:12:05,070 --> 00:12:05,950
And why are you here?

233
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,600
Right now, you should focus on

234
00:12:08,070 --> 00:12:10,310
those guests instead of me.

235
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:11,520
Need you tell me that?

236
00:12:11,910 --> 00:12:13,270
I’ve had maids go get Physician Zhang.

237
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,950
That takes time

238
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:18,360
which you don’t have,
because His Majesty

239
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:21,520
is waiting for Princess Royal now.

240
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:24,310
During Count Rong’s last visit,

241
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,240
I overheard him

242
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,400
arguing with Her Highness.

243
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:29,550
We must be careful.

244
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,070
Come on in, Physician Zhang!

245
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,640
Check on my grandmother!

246
00:12:48,190 --> 00:12:49,640
She isn’t in a coma for long.

247
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,550
There’s medicine to wake her up.

248
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:52,720
Good.

249
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:59,640
Dissolve it in warm water
and feed it to her.

250
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,640
Got it.

251
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:05,550
Her Highness has asked me

252
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,550
to keep her condition secret.

253
00:13:06,670 --> 00:13:07,640
I should leave.

254
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,880
Sure. Take care.

255
00:13:09,150 --> 00:13:10,360
Your help won’t be forgotten.

256
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:21,310
This is odd.

257
00:13:21,310 --> 00:13:23,360
The medicine is darker than before.

258
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,310
We’re running out of time.

259
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:37,540
<i>General-in-chief of the State’s Tablet
Princess Royal Dening’s Tablet</i>

260
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,600
What did you do, Count Cheng’an?

261
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,120
Zhang,

262
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,480
how come

263
00:13:56,910 --> 00:13:58,670
Princess Royal hasn’t shown up yet?

264
00:13:58,880 --> 00:13:59,640
Father,

265
00:14:00,070 --> 00:14:01,950
I have no idea, either.

266
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,720
Really?

267
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:05,520
Brother,

268
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:08,270
how could you not know

269
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,720
as the organizer of the banquet?

270
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:14,120
Is something wrong?

271
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:22,190
Princess Ban and Count Rong
aren’t here, either.

272
00:14:22,790 --> 00:14:24,600
Do you also not know where they are?

273
00:14:25,270 --> 00:14:27,000
If Crown Prince

274
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:29,400
can’t get hold of a few people,

275
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,670
how can he rule the entire state?

276
00:14:32,790 --> 00:14:33,520
Brother,

277
00:14:35,190 --> 00:14:37,240
Great-aunt is yet to be seen.

278
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:39,520
If she doesn’t receive
birthday congratulations in time

279
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,120
and her health is affected,

280
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:43,910
can you

281
00:14:44,430 --> 00:14:46,310
take that responsibility?

282
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:56,760
Please be patient, Your Majesty.

